Date Posted: 2014/05/03 05:02:05Ref. JB1001843319
HR and Administration AssistantBin Murshed Holding
•Assist the HR Manager and HR Team in day to day operations for expat and local staff
•Ensuring starters are set up,
sending out information,
requesting references
•Producing staff contracts for local staff
•Update and maintain records in the personnel information system and run standard and ad hoc queries
•Prepare various kinds of HR related correspondence
•Assist with visa applications,
cancellation and transfer
•Maintain and update personnel files
•Maintain leave administration
Skills
•Intermediate vocational training (preferably on HR and/or Administration)
•At least two years of working experience in a comparable position
•Operational HR experience
•Basic understanding of HR processes and procedures
•Knowledge of MS Office (including using MS Access)
•Fluent in Arabic and English (spoken and written)
•Persuasive and result oriented
